data.description: Imagine being able to own a property living the style at your own comfort with no restrictions. Being able to enjoy peaceful quiet nights looking up at the sky and see the beautiful bright stars shining over your property. Welcome to this beautiful new traditional built home with a bonus of 5 plus acres. 1900 sqft plus home with four bedrooms and two full bathrooms, an open concept living room and kitchen with decorative bright lighting. New electric stove amongst with built in white cabinets with smooth granite countertops. Outstanding master bedroom with a double vanity restroom set up and a huge walk in closet. The home has energy efficient items such as a heat pump system and filled in with foam insulation.
